ander ii of russia                grand duchess maria alexandrovna of russia                        princess marie of hesse and by rhine                michael of romania                                          christian ix of denmark                george i of greece                        princess louise of hessekassel                constantine i of greece                              grand duke constantine nikolayevich of russia                grand duchess olga constantinovna of russia                        princess alexandra of saxealtenburg                princess helen of greece and denmark                                    william i german emperor                frederick iii german emperor                        princess augusta of saxeweimareisenach                princess sophia of prussia                              prince albert of saxecoburg and gotha                  victoria princess royal                        victoria queen of the united kingdom               see also kings of romania communist romania line of succession to the romanian throne references  world war ii –  years after former romanian monarch remembers decision to switch sides radiofreeeuroperadioliberty retrieved  december    looking for leadership human events retrieved  december    peter kurth michael of romania peterkurthcom  a b craig s smith  january  romanias king without a throne outlives foes and setbacks the new york times retrieved  december    a b ms regele mihai i retrieved  december    bucur marie carol ii pages  from balkan strongmen dictators and authoritarian rulers of south eastern europe edited by bernd jürgen fischer west lafayette purdue university press  page   rulers of romania rulers retrieved  july    fotodocument mihai mare voievod de alba iulia  romania libera retrieved  december    ce citeau românii acum  de ani ziua  november   a b fundamental rules of the royal family of romania the romanian royal family website as retrieved  january   in romanian t