io books fabian sklar  king michael h fabian  fabian sklar  king michael h fabian as founding shareholder of fabian sklar  king pc michael h fabian has won numerous cases throughout his  year career that have created groundbreaking national precedent in establishing and protecting the rights of policyholders for clients ranging from homeowners to fortune  companies a nationally recognized expert on insurance law he is an editor of michigan insurance law and practice published by the institute for continuing legal education icle as well as coauthor of the chapter on property insurance law he also authored the fire insurance chapter in icle’s causes of action formbook a frequent lecturer on property insurance issues to numerous legal and professional groups throughout the country michael has also served as an appointed member of the national fire protection association’s technical committee on fire investigations which publishes nfpa  guide for fire and explosion investigations the authoritative text on fire investigations and on the insurance law committee of the state bar of michigan in recognition of his achievements in advancing the rights of homeowners and business owners after fires and property damage claims michigan lawyers weekly magazine honored michael as a  “leader in the law” an accomplishment presented to only  attorneys throughout michigan best lawyers magazine named michael its insurance law “lawyer of the year” for  this is the second time the legal publication has selected michael for this honor which is awarded annually to one lawyer in each practice area in local communities michael has also been selected as a michigan “super lawyer” by super lawyers magazine every year since  a “top lawyer” by dbusiness magazine and a “best lawyer in america” in insurance law by best lawyers magazine he is a member of the oakland county bar association american bar association tort and insurance practice section american bar association property insurance committee state bar of michigan michigan association of justice american association of justice and the wayne county mediation tribunal he earned a ba with honors from the james madison college of michigan state university and a jd from the university of detroit school of law               mfabianfabiansklarcom published works causes of action formbook chapter on fire loss claims institute for continuing legal education icle   michigan insurance law and practice chapter on property insurance institute for continuing legal education icle   michigan insurance law and practice editor institute for continuing legal education icle   published cases griswold properties llc v lexington ins co  mich app   nwd   revd in part  mich app   nw d   app den  mich   nwd   salesin v state farm fire  casualty  mich app   nwd   williams v auto club insurance  mich app   nwd   borman v state farm fire and gas co  mich app   nwd   affd  mich   nwd   smith v michigan basic  mich   nw d   ponder v allstate ins co  e supp  ed mich  michael h kings badges  microsoft dynamics community try microsoft edge a fast and secure browser thats designed for windows  no thanks get started cloud platform stories datacenters microsoft azure find a solution provider mobility enterprise mobility office mobility windows mobility microsoft surface microsoft lumia productivity office office  for business plans and pricing office  for smb office  for enterprise skype for business microsoft dynamics  overview pricing and licensing microsoft dynamics ax microsoft dynamics gp microsoft dynamics nav microsoft dynamics sl windows windows  for business windows  for internet of things windows devices data and analytics microsoft sql server microsoft power bi microsoft cortana intelligence suite operations management operations management suite system center sign in search microsoft search dynamics community dynamics community participate ask a question get started badges earn badges view badges leaderboards compete on leade